summary:
Leith is a character generated by BellaGail\'s \"Better Females by Bella\" MOD.

This save is taken just after character creation, before the execution part...
descriptionHtml:
There are 2 mods required this character to look same as the screenshot;

1.Better Females by Bella (http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812)

And additional optional file of the same awesome mod must be installed (they are provided under the same link above)

2.Makeup version 2

Depending on your taste you can experiment on other makeup options from Bella\'s mod



-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Simply put the savegame file in your Skyrim savegame folder.Save file is taken in the beginning of the game, just after character creation.




Feel free to share or modify, credits are always appriciated and pls give credits to Bellagail for creating \"Better Females by Bella\" as well...
author: fgmsilencer
